data.description: SELLER WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE UP TO $5,000 TOWARDS BUYERaS CLOSING COST! Welcome to your new stick built home in the country. Home has been renovated and you will love all the updates. Step into spacious living room that is open to dining area, great for entertaining. Kitchen has beautiful upgrades including new backsplash and granite countertops. Owner's suite has large closet and en-suite bathroom. There are two additional bedrooms and one additional bathroom. Home sits on large private lot of 2.58 acres. Property is located just 10 minutes from I85, restaurants, and Lake Hartwell!
